PrecisAmendment to the LAURENTIAN PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS, 1992 which will permit the Authority to recover its administrative expenses for pilot boat services where they are provided by contractors, as well as at Les Escoumins, where the Authority itself operates the boats.
